VALUES (185, 'Single Leg Circle Jump Rope Video Exercise Guide', 'Calves', 'Conditioning', 'Jump Rope', 'Compound',
        'Push (Unilateral)', 'Intermediate', 'Forearms', 'The single leg circle jump rope is a variation of the jump rope and a cardio exercise used to condition the entire body.
