Rotate the wrists to generate velocity and help the rope revolve around the body.
As the rope moves toward your feet, hop with one leg to allow it to pass underneath.
When you land, try to move in a clockwise or counterclockwise fashion and complete a circle as you jump.
Repeat for the desired number of repetitions or time.', 'Remember to reverse the direction of the hops and also incorporate both directions on each leg.
